heading: 2. The 27th day of October 2020 is appointed to be the establishment day
text_raw:
2. The 27th day of October 2020 is appointed to be the establishment day 

for the purposes of the CervicalCheck Tribunal Act 2019 (No. 31 of 2019). 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

21 October, 2020. 

STEPHEN DONNELLY, 
Minister for Health. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 23rd October, 2020.

text_raw:
EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation) 

This Order appoints the 27th day of October 2020 as the establishment day of 
the CervicalCheck Tribunal under Section 4 of the CervicalCheck Tribunal Act 
2019, for the purpose of hearing and determining claims arising from 
CervicalCheck.
